**Image Title:** "The Dragon Reborn Stands Tall"

**Description:** This dramatic landscape photograph captures the essence of Rand al'Thor, is standing at the edge of a windswept cliff, (perhaps in the Mountains of Dhoom), gazing out upon a stormy horizon.
The sky above is ablaze with hues of fiery orange and crimson, an ominous portent of the Last Battle to come.

Rand, in the foreground, stands strong against the tempestuous backdrop, his determination etched on his face.
Rand,q, stands tall,ning confidently, a gleaming heron-marked sword by his side.
